I think the Dark Elves are Racial, Ideological, <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> and</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Religious enemies to other elvenkind.  I may be talking nonsense, but this is how I see it:<br>
<br>
Racial-<br>
Dark Elves are Dark Elves.  The very antithesis of normal Elves.  If you want to go further, they are cruel and ruthless, and the Teir'Dal empire seeks to dominate the whole of Norrath, including the Elven territories.  Those who do not submit are to perish.<br>
<br>
Ideological-<br>
This does not fit the form for all Dark Elves, but for those who are either loyal to Neriak or Innoruuk, their beleif are either of conquest or hatred.  The Elves of Norrath seek neither, and the followers of Tunare seek balance, or so you say.  Personally I think they seek the preservation of life and Karana seek balance, but that is me.<br>
<br>
Religious-<br>
Lets not forget WHY there are Dark Elves.  It goes right back to quibling amongst the gods.  Innoruuk was jealous of being left out of the pack between Tunare, Zek, and Brell.  Instead of attacking the Neutral Brell, or his Ally (or atleast fellow tyrant) Zek, he instead seeks to punish the goodly Tunare by capturing the King and Queen of the Elven empire and torturing them for 300 years in the Plane of Hate.  After that, he deposited them back on Norrath and they returned to their empire, spreading the word of Innoruuk.  The story goes on, but I don't feel like summarizing it.  It can all be found at <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.tomeofages.com">www.tomeofages.com</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.  This is a good place to go for EQ lore, and not just because it is run by someone who was in DeVir <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->    It's a really good, long story.  Read up on it, find out why we exist, why we hate you Elves so much, and why we're blue <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p><B><font color="darkred">Velve D'Verin</font><Br>
